ants arising\ncorrespond to those obtained in the dual conformal invariant momentum twistor\nversion of the formalism, but differences arise in the specification of the\nboundary terms. Surprisingly, in this framework, some finite loop integrals can\nbe performed as simply as those for tree diagrams.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2011 19:42:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2011 19:06:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Apr 2011 15:02:50 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2012 13:04:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
