ds from extremal set theory, we prove\nthat these Kneser hypergraphs have unbounded chromatic number. This generalizes\na result of Szemer\\'edi for graphs and might be of independent interest. Many\nopen problems remain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2011 02:24:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Sep 2011 20:05:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2011 02:21:29 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 24 Jul 2013 21:31:47 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2013 20:06:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
