uld be more sensitive\nthan the type-I pair (or, in general, $n$-tuplet) methods because of its\nmultifilter construction and its independence from $n$.}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2011 08:53:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 13 Mar 2011 05:14:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 16 Apr 2011 00:10:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-04-19"}
